	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>My low ranked and low income 26th lvl Druid was fighting ranger style all week in EK trying to get one of these belts. Between the KS, people paying 500pp for looting rights so they didn't have to fight for one and the just plain out and out mob scene, I was lucky one of my kills finally resulted in a belt. Any announcement of a belt was immediately met with a swarm of Druids (usually 20-30 of them) all trying to loot it.<br><br>It's much nicer than what I had and I'm finally getting my wisdom up to a respectable level.<br><br>Shame on all those that got thier belt by paying for looting rights and/or KS. I earned mine by fighting.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
